			When we have to make our budgets smaller, we do not, however, want to lose the joy of purchasing. Smaller budget can even make purchase more exciting, because we will start to look for good things of lower prices than we previously expected. Get fed up with old evening dresses in the cabinet? Just buy a new one online. Do not worry — you can make it within budget. Presuming that most of us acknowledge the convenience of purchasing online, here are a few tips on how to get a satisfying new evening dress from an online dress store within a much smaller budget than before. 
<br />;<img src="http://www.pan.net/en/p/oo/182451649_12878794_49181855.jpg" />;
<br />;<br />;The first thing to do is obviously to find out the right store. Many people only go to brand name stores, but if we search for "<a href="http://en.pan.netcom/go/out/url=-aHR0cDovL3d3dy5hdWRyZXNzZm9yZm9ybWFsLmNvbS8_" target="_blank">;formal dresses</a>;" or "<a href="http://en.pan.netcom/go/out/url=-aHR0cDovL3d3dy5hdWRyZXNzZm9yZm9ybWFsLmNvbS9ldmVuaW5nLWRyZXNzZXM_" target="_blank">;cheap evening dresses</a>;" in Google, we can find that there are tens of thousands of online stores selling all kinds of evening dresses at much lower prices than brand name stores. The tip is to choose those can be found on Twitter, Facebook and YouTube, as good stores are always willing to communicate with their customers through every possible social media network. Online support system and free customer service line are also important things, because that will be the major means customers can reach the stores. If you are not sure about anything, try first to get through the service number to make sure the service is always available when you are in need. If you have no idea on what to ask for the first call, you may just try to figure out how fast they can deliver the dresses. If the store has warehouse located in your country, 24-48 hours are good; and if not, one week should be reasonable. In fact, in order to compete with those brand name stores, these non-brand-name stores are always quick in responding and deliver every order as fast as they so that customers will trust them for more purchases.
<br />;<br />;Since a good store is chosen, the next thing is to choose from the various exhibiting dress images. Images are always illusive, but prices are reliable. Why these non-brand-name stores claim that they sell the cheapest evening dresses? The answer is they offer dresses of different price ranges. The most expensive products are possibly in the "over $500" group, and the cheapest ones may be placed in the "under $100" range. As a result, customers can always find something they like very much yet within their budget. Even the “high-class” evening dresses are still much cheaper than similar ones being sold in brand name stores. Well, not every dress designer can get high pay and considerable fame and have their designs being sold in big stores at decent prices.
<br />;<img src="http://www.pan.net/en/p/oo/182451649_3394009_49181859.jpg" />;
<br />;Attention: do not get over-excited for the low prices and overlook details. You should never hesitate to bother the online service persons for everything you care about – from size to product material, from whether the dress matches your shoes to what kind of extra accessories you can get, and even whether discount is available for your next purchase or referring friends. It can be expected that all of your reasonable demands will be met as long as the store believes that they get a returning customer.
